## Protocol Overview

BeatLand is a festival NFT ecosystem on Ethereum. Users purchase tiered ERC1155 passes (GENERAL / VIP / BACKSTAGE), attend virtual performances to earn BEAT ERC20 tokens, and redeem unique memorabilia NFTs by burning BEAT tokens. A single FestivalPass contract handles both pass NFTs (token IDs 1–3) and memorabilia NFTs (IDs encoded as `collectionId << 128 + itemId`).

